name: ✨ Celebration of 100 Stories Told ✨
description:
The Crown 👑 The birth place of the first word.
A Century.
An evolution experience in prose, culture, story art and verbal imagery.
Here is a gratitude statement to all whom have indulged the storyteller.
Light the way.
Say the words.
Give Thanks.
Blessings to all whom know of the tellings of stories from the tribes of old and new. Past,present and future.
